text: René Schroeder (23 December 1920 - 10 February 2001) was a Luxembourgian gymnast. He competed at the 1948 Summer Olympics and the 1952 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1920 births Category:2001 deaths Category:Luxembourgian male artistic gymnasts Category:Olympic gymnasts of Luxembourg Category:Gymnasts at the 1948 Summer Olympics Category:Gymnasts at the 1952 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Esch-sur-Alzette
